== Introduction 
SiteFuel is a Ruby program 

Use SiteFuel to:
  * deploy your website out of SVN or GIT
  * minify your 


== System Requirements

  * Ruby 1.8.6


== Installation

SiteFuel is deployed a RubyGem through http://gemcutter.org. You should be able to install it directly using RubyGems:

     $ gem install -t sitefuel

You can also download a ZIP-file containing SiteFuel and all of the gems it depends on from http://sitefuel.org/download/sitefuel-complete.zip



